<plot>Gladys is a timid girl who wants assurance that her sweetheart is not a descendant of the pirate Captain Kidd. She goes to a fake spiritualist. Meanwhile, her sweetheart gets mixed up with a bunch of waiters, dressed up as pirates aboard a ship. He is forced to change clothes with one of them, and Gladys shows up.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?359110</url></doc>
